Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Style,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[OP]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:30.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇と遊ぶ星たちへ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:35.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛を歌い　飽きつくした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:40.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏を灯し　雛菊の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:45.87,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢に寄り添う爪の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:53.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唇から唇へと伝い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:58.50,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その温もりはどこへ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:05.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辿り付くあてはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:11.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたでなくちゃ　満たせない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私じゃなきゃ　許せなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:20.45,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　私はこの足で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:25.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ぞっとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飼い殺しなら　救われる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:34.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でも見事に　鍵は外れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:45.45,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私はまるで　鳥籠を欲している狂う籠鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:53.25,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘を抱いた花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:30.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与黑暗游戏的星斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:35.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为爱咏唱　我已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:40.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点亮夏季的雏菊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:45.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴随梦境的爪痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:53.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过双唇传递而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:58.50,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份温存将何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:05.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有可以前往的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:11.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你　我得不到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:15.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我　是不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:20.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能用自己的双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.66,0:01:22.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:25.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却感到心惊胆寒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果养我一生　我还可以得救
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:34.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　锁却顺利打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:45.45,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宛如为渴求鸟笼而疯狂的笼中之鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:53.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀抱谎言的花

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Style,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[ED]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:55.36,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見てて　ご覧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:23:01.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほら　満ちぬけた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:05.96,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溢れた傍から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:11.79,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えて　抜け殻に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:21.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流されて　辿り付く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:27.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現　蕩ける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:33.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天この魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:44.29,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢　紡いだ夢を　どうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:53.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その小指に絡めなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:57.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛んだ刺は
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.63,0:24:03.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一つ抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取る　抜ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:55.36,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注意看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.61,0:23:01.01,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊　充满了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.08,0:23:05.96,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从溢出的一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:11.79,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐消失　变成了空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.63,0:23:21.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随波逐流　到达彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:27.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉醉于现实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:33.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:44.29,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦　编织的梦境　请看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:53.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请缠绕我的小指不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.62,0:23:57.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛的刺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.63,0:24:03.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根被拔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.52,0:24:08.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取出　拔掉

Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山河三岔路 别离之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要保护的是自己 是他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是常世的黑暗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非对错无法补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有终结的深仇大恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭转时空 打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难报之怨 我为您报

Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}无论是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}绝对无法逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}天上的鸟儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.88,0:02:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秃子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗 秃子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢 什么时候回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你呢 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我  谁叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}终于长大成人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}明知道他是个坏男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我还是想和他共度良宵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 是恶作剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\a6}不忘感谢之心 礼仪端正典雅 循规蹈矩地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\a6}丹下虫 真让人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你画的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御影 高杉 上课时乱写乱画
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会写在你们的升学报告书里的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经初中三年级了 太没紧张感了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会后悔莫及的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:05:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 平石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 是我画的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吗 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和柚木 秋惠无关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把刚刚写的话删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想中考落榜的话 好好听讲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是在吓唬你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要告他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹下老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从以前就不喜欢那家伙 有点小事马上就记在记事本上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋惠 你爸爸认识校长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要告诉校长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像丹下这么阴险的老师 必须把他赶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你爸爸说说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人做班主任的话 真的会中考落榜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了 逸子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今已经有3个人中考落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那个记事本 肯定没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有3人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从学长那里听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 秋惠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 这关系到我们的将来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在偷听学生的谈话吗 曾根老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是高雅的兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太嚣张了 石又老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐为什么要回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要呆在这个学校就能知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 秃子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了 山童
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你陪这个麻烦的家伙 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.54,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 再说一遍试试
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山童 帮我拧一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发条完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有实体 所以附在玩具上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫她公主啊 山童
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让我这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菊里公主 要叫我公主 这个色眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心我把你绑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拧好了 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山童是个好孩子 我让你做我的家臣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托了 秋惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋惠 真的会和她爸爸说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是说了 但他说没有证据是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹下老师不会真写在升学报告书上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为 爸爸也是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想继续了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋惠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木不会逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会相信丹下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想把他赶出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到证据 然后交给校长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据  是那个记事本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要制造一个比那种东西更好的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制造
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 信已经放在他的鞋柜里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要说是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 又要被他记下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就肯定考不上高中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 其实我是想吸引老师的注意才恶作剧的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请当面训斥我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一定会开开心心地过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去就很没经验嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 那家伙一来我就抱住他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把旅馆的招牌也一起拍进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗他人是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能拍到我的脸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木 躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸子 你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是个小孩 在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老师  丹下老师告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\a6}你的怨恨，由我来消除。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 决不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 决不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱 少女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山童
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的想报怨 就解开这根红线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开红线 你就和我正式结下了契约
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人会当即被冲入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被冲入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报怨后 你自身也要付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人必害己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约生效后 你的灵魂也会堕入地狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会堕入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那是你死后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂会饱受痛苦 永远徘徊于地狱中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么为了那种家伙 连我也要下地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后由你来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 地狱少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 刚刚的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你看到的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在你之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平石 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是摔坏了 可是要你赔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没收
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平石逸子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管她 御影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}再见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了 一直咕咕叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被没收的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在家也是一边听那个一边学习的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以上课也不能专心听讲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你在写什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被记下来的话 就认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经三年级了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要写到升学报告书上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要告诉家长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负学生很好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负 不对的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我中考落榜 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说老师至今让3个人中考落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己不喜欢的学生 老师就像这样摆出权力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好缓解自己的压力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决不能中考落榜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂也会堕入地狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么 平石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你要诅咒我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西太无聊了 你都初中三年级了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是2哦 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 好像是活的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉伯数字在阿拉伯语中 好像被称为印度数字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 所以才这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样都好 快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蜂的一刺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要请你下地狱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惹了别人的怨恨啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是为学生着想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个年纪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被黑暗迷惑的悲哀之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害他人 贬低他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪孽中的罪恶灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死一次试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆周率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.141592653589793238462626433832795028841971
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个怨恨 我会把它冲入地狱的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逸子 终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 丹下老师让我还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他笑着说 要是再拿到学校来就给你扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹下老师果然是个好老师哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 不是丹下老师的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹下老师的记事本上不要说名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一个文字都没有写
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 逸子转学了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.47,0:22:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 由我来消除

Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Style,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[预告]
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.95,0:24:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.44,0:24:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北山明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.64,0:24:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.91,0:24:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人正忍受着痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.04,0:24:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出来也出不来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.03,0:24:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.40,0:24:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍冷静一下头脑 怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.51,0:24:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拯救那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.19,0:24:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 把他冲入地狱去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.13,0:24:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.44,0:24:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 笼中鸟
